   - Add `.clear-btn:hover { color: #e6e6e6; }`

4. Visibility toggling via `:placeholder-shown` (no JavaScript needed). The icon and button are SIBLINGS after the input, so the general sibling combinator `~` works:
   - Default state (input empty / placeholder shown): show search icon, hide clear button:
     ```css
     .search-wrapper .clear-btn { display: none; }
     ```
   - When input has text (placeholder NOT shown): hide search icon, show clear button:
     ```css
     .search-wrapper input:not(:placeholder-shown) ~ .search-icon { display: none; }
